sequenceDiagram

participant U as User (React)
participant A as Admin (React)
participant N as NestJS API
participant G as Go Service
participant Q as BullMQ Queue
participant P as PostgreSQL
participant M as MongoDB

%% --- User places order ---
U->>N: Place Order (REST API)

%% --- Address validation (gRPC) ---
N->>G: CheckServiceability(pincode)
G->>M: Query delivery zones
M-->>G: Zone data
G-->>N: serviceable / eta

%% --- Save order ---
N->>P: Save Order

%% --- Async job ---
N->>Q: Publish job (order_created)
Q->>G: Consume job

%% --- Background processing ---
G->>M: Store logs / receipt

%% --- Real-time logs (SSE) ---
G-->>A: Stream logs (SSE)

%% --- Real-time notifications (WebSocket) ---
G-->>U: Order status update
G-->>A: Order status update

%% --- Final response ---
N-->>U: Order Success Response